            <button id="submit-btn" onclick="submitQuiz()" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
                🎯 إنهاء الاختبار وعرض النتائج
